With one note actors, or talented comedic actors wasted saying shit dialogue and acting ghetto, its pathetic! How about trying to appeal to intelligent, educated minorities too Hollywood? Sisters, Bad Moms, Office Party, etc. Just a recycling of Hangover, over and over! I mean why won't the studios take any chances anymore? Where is the Beverly Hills Cop, Midnight Run, My Cousin Vinny, Stripes, Caddyshack, Silver Streak, Bustin Loose, etc. There is a reason Adam Sandler's popularity dissipated over time and it's not just his age!  Oh and that Amy Schumer looking actress who's shtick is that she is angry all the time and curses! She fuckin sucks! Speaking of Bateman, at least Horrible Bosses was somewhat original!
